You think you'll ruin the atmosphere? "Who told you that?"

You think you're a waste of space? "Who told you that?"

You think that people will make fun of you once you fail? "Who told you that?

These are just some scenarios that helped me overcome some anxieties I've had

So the video mentioned "What were the reasons you shouldn't play alone, who told you that?"

It all makes sense HAHAHAHHAHAH nobody was telling me shit about that, it was just all in my head.

I just wanted to rant about this since it helps in a lot of situations.
